title: 17 Books On WW2 Tanks
description:
The following torrent contains:

D-Day Tank Warfare
D-Day to Berlin- Armor Camouflage and Markings of the United States, British, and German Armies
Encyclopedia of German Tanks of WW2
Germany's Tiger Tanks- Design, Production & Modifications
Russian Tanks of WWII
Images of Kursk, History's Greatest Tank Battle
Images of War- Panzer Divisions at War 1939-1945
Inside The Great Tanks
M3 Medium Tank vs Panzer III
Osprey- Kingtiger Heavy Tank 1942.1945
Panther VS T34
Panzers En Normandie 1
Sherman Firefly VS Tiger
Soviet Tanks In Combat 1941- The T-28, T-34, T-34-85 and T-44 Medium Tanks
Tank Battles of The Pacific War 1941-1945
The M4 Sherman At War- The European Theatre 1942-1945
VW at War (German Trucks and Cars in World War II, Vol 2)
